{"tid":2285659,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇：政府應資助確診患者入院期間的工資","createTime":"2020-11-14T09:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T10:20:03.000Z","uid":212626,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"04739ae083295c1a1858a7c0a0a09ff1b9cb9b9d","tid":2285659,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:42:48.000Z","msg":"<strong>袁國勇倡政府資助確診者工資以增市民檢測誘因 </strong><br />\n<br />\n袁國勇又指，有病徵的人士到私家醫生求診，只有不足20%自願接受新型冠狀病毒檢測，認為私家醫生的檢測率偏低。他今早與當局會面，曾商討能否增加市民接受檢測的誘因，例如資助確診患者入院期間的工資，以提升私家醫生的病毒檢測比率。他同時質疑經常進行全民檢測的成本效益，指香港難以像內地般進行封閉式小區管理，認為除了政府鼓勵或強制市民檢測外，市民亦應以手機應用程式協助追蹤病毒源頭，呼籲市民拍照記下曾光顧的食肆及的士車牌，以便追蹤確診患者。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366261\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2366261&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNyzmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=92a736bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366261</a>"},{"pid":"cea47360801b01e75fcef89bb5347247da0c4721","tid":2285659,"uid":365024,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:43:15.000Z","msg":"悶得滯？"},{"pid":"1adad104067732fe0ab38b268e49c943296ec4c6","tid":2285659,"uid":47697,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:43:18.000Z","msg":"樓豬無問題答就開新post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8887a726f74d04c0f2c7978a993ab250db2b79","tid":2285659,"uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:43:42.000Z","msg":"我的訴求是上班"},{"pid":"ecbf597d09482404bbc2af6ad0d4d0ae87297b4f","tid":2285659,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T09:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfef37ff0121d1aca1170468c7a95349732a27b1","tid":2285659,"uid":212626,"like":3,"dis